::Shadow Wing::
She soared above their head with her wings stretched out and gently gliding 
on the breeze staying at thier side while heading to the Maximal base 
through the forest.  Her Great Owl mode looked powerful and yet soft and 
delicate.  Her feathers were varios shades of gray from dark to light.  Her 
talons were sharp and tucked up under her belly while flying.  Her deep 
golden optics peirced through the dark so she could see in near total 
darkness.  She effortlessly glided in and out of the trees keeping up with 
the other two bots, Ramulus and Striker. She turned and looked at Ramulus.
"How much further until we reach your base? You look like you can use a CR 
chamber right now."
